title: Hazel v2.0 - Multi-Concept Creative WordPress Theme
description:
Hazel is multi-purpose, clean, creative, retina ready, responsive WordPress theme ideal for creative use, photography, portfolio showcase, modern businesses, agency, fashion, blog, shop, personal use, etc. Hazel is highly customizable theme with unlimited combinations of header layouts, title area layouts, mega menu, side menu and tons of shortcodes. With powerful and flexible theme options, included page builder, it gives freedom to create beautiful web sites and unlimited number of different page layouts.

Hazel comes with 32 amazing ready-to-use demo sites.

Product page: http://themeforest.net/item/hazel-multiconcept-creative-wordpress-theme/8146099

This wordpress theme has been fully nulled, to install simply upload it to your host like you would any other wordpress theme.
